## ‚ö° Funcionalidades

* ‚úÖ **Autentica√ß√£o unificada** (OAuth Installed ou Service Account)

* ‚úÖ **Token reutiliz√°vel** (`token_json`)

* ‚úÖ Servi√ßos prontos:

  * **Gmail** ‚Üí listar, enviar e-mails, anexos
  * **Drive** ‚Üí upload, busca, exclus√£o
  * **Calendar** ‚Üí criar/listar eventos (com Google Meet)
  * **Pub/Sub** ‚Üí t√≥picos, subscriptions, publish/pull
  * **Cloud Storage** ‚Üí upload/download, listar, deletar, copiar/mover, URL assinada

* ‚úÖ Suporte a **Domain-Wide Delegation** para Service Accounts

* ‚úÖ Compat√≠vel com **Poetry** e **pip**

